{"tid":2401962,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基零片酬撐本地創作拍《遺愛》入圍大阪亞洲電影節爭獎","createTime":"2021-02-10T06:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T15:06:25.000Z","uid":245286,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17f55156e35cf5981e1cbed72d12bfaeba4380c9","tid":2401962,"uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"//早前憑劇集《暖男爸爸》成為民選視帝的鄭中基，參與的新作《遺愛》，同樣為了支持新導演及本地創作，這套鄭中基零片酬演出的作品今日收到好消息，入圍今屆大阪亞洲電影節競賽組別，將與來自十多個國家的電影競逐最佳電影，影片將於下月在當地舉行世界首映。//<br />\n<br />\n（其實我比較想快啲睇到《阿龍》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210209/XN5PPYEBYBHK7LYSARKS5AJJWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210209%2FXN5PPYEBYBHK7LYSARKS5AJJWI%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=68f69c75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210209%2FXN5PPYEBYBHK7LYSARKS5AJJWI%2F&h=d5f15bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210209/XN5PPYEBYBHK7LYSARKS5AJJWI/</a>"},{"pid":"95a2948a41418b0e1d46548ac8f62572c7347665","tid":2401962,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T22:35:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e25980ce98b39971951ff77c61b4d3db481793ae","tid":2401962,"uid":139611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T22:47:07.000Z","msg":"暴龍仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27cda9946a835aab95d15f49d1734b54ce88103","tid":2401962,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4960d3813463e473963416e6340e0772a4cc595e","tid":2401962,"uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"之前睇過簡介<br />\n故事好似係改編自當年屯門大興邨醃